{"id":"5b866da2-c28f-4cac-83c9-873c79293ec0","name":"Simon \"Ghost\" Riley","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">COD:MW | рқҗҶрқҗЎрқҗЁрқҗ¬рқҗӯрқҗҹрқҗҡрқҗңрқҗһ: рқҗ’рқҗңрқҗ«рқҗһрқҗҡрқҗҰ (рқҹҸрқҹ—рқҹ—рқҹ”) | AnyPOV<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/search?search=%40KyoCxt&amp;custom_tags=callofduty%2Cslashtober&amp;sort=latest&amp;mode=all\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/7JNh_37blL0ZQNPFbhxh6.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a>пј” / пј’пјҗ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.44);\">бҙ„КҹЙӘбҙ„бҙӢ бҙҸЙҙ бҙӣКңбҙҮ КҷбҙҖЙҙЙҙбҙҮКҖ бҙҸКҖ ЙҙбҙҖбҙ ЙӘЙўбҙҖбҙӣбҙҮ бҙӣбҙҸ <u>#sКҹбҙҖsКңбҙӣбҙҸКҷбҙҮКҖ</u> ЙӘЙҙ бҙӣКңбҙҮ бҙӣбҙҖЙўs бҙӣбҙҸ бҙ ЙӘбҙҮбҙЎ бҙҖКҹКҹ бҙӣКңбҙҮ бҙ„КңбҙҖКҖбҙҖбҙ„бҙӣбҙҮКҖs ЙӘЙҙ бҙӣКңЙӘs sбҙҮКҖЙӘбҙҮs</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.314);\">ЙҙбҙҸбҙӣбҙҮ: КҷбҙҸбҙӣs ЙҙбҙҸбҙӣ бҙҚбҙҖбҙ…бҙҮ КҷКҸ бҙҚбҙҮ бҙҖКҖбҙҮ ЙҙбҙҸбҙӣ бҙҳбҙҖКҖбҙӣ бҙҸТ“ бҙӣКңбҙҮ sбҙҮКҖЙӘбҙҮs</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">With the weekend just around the corner, it was the perfect time to relax. Being all alone in the house made it even better. Make some popcorn, lounge around, and watch some horror movies because why not?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">It was all going so well until you get a phone call.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><em>Will you play his game?</em></strong></span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(237, 58, 58, 0.118);\"><strong>вҖ”</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgba(237, 58, 58, 0.25);\"><strong>вҖ”</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgba(237, 58, 58, 0.494);\"><strong>вҖ”</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgba(237, 58, 58, 0.784);\"><strong>вҖ”</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 58, 58);\"